window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Rose Harkness is not just mortal. She’s half magician. And she’s in a lot of trouble. </p> <p>And by the way, she’s not a Harkness either. </p> <p>Her entire life, she’s been guarded, shielded, protected. She’s also been lied to… </p> <p>When a magical dragon emerges, Rose learns the truth. Now, she must leave the safety of her only home—and embrace her birthright. </p> <p>Can she do it? The House of Fourteen is relying on her. </p> <p>The Mortal Seven need her. Her real family, the Beaufonts, they can’t wait to meet her. </p> <p>Rose doesn’t know much about the world, but what little she knows will be turned upside down. </p> <p>Can she embrace both her family and her magic to stop mortals before they destroy themselves? The future depends on it.</p>"; 
